{"id":1645,"date":"2025-06-30T12:20:52","date_gmt":"2025-06-30T05:20:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/?p=1645"},"modified":"2025-06-30T12:22:03","modified_gmt":"2025-06-30T05:22:03","slug":"1645-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/1645-2\/","title":{"rendered":"ECOLUX CITY: T\u00c2M \u0110I\u1ec2M M\u1edaI TRONG L\u00c0N S\u00d3NG \u0110\u00d4 TH\u1eca H\u00d3A B\u00ccNH D\u01af\u01a0NG"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>Vi\u1ec7c s\u00e1t nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ecba gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd v\u00e0o TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &#8220;V\u00e0nh \u0111ai \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u2013 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p&#8221;, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u00e1c &#8220;v\u1ec7 tinh&#8221; \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb ki\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thu\u1ed9c tam gi\u00e1c kinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi TP HCM v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed3ng Nai, s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ee5m b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb th\u1ebf th\u00f4ng qua s\u1ee9c b\u1eadt m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n kinh t\u1ebf t\u1ec9nh, duy tr\u00ec tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u1ea1i d\u1ecbch. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng giao th\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh, ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng gi\u00fap B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef v\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed top \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat v\u1ed1n FDI t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">D\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c s\u1eb5n c\u00f3 Th\u1ee7 D\u1ea7u M\u1ed9t &#8211; trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 m\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1ec7 tinh sau Th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb th\u00f4ng minh, c\u00e1p ng\u1ea7m, trung t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh, 5G, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb v\u1ec7 tinh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1649\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"485\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-1-1.jpg 360w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-1-1-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 647px) 100vw, 647px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng TP M\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sau s\u00e1t nh\u1eadp, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 s\u1ebd th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5c giao th\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c (v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 3, 4; Metro, cao t\u1ed1c; c\u1ea3ng bi\u1ec3n\u2026) hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 nhanh h\u01a1n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed3ng gh\u00e9p v\u00e0o quy ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng k\u00e9p c\u1ee7a Tp. HCM, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn Metro n\u1ed1i t\u1eeb Su\u1ed1i Ti\u00ean \u2013 trung t\u00e2m B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i di chuy\u1ec3n trong \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh n\u00f3i chung.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1647\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-2.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"871\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-2.webp 480w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-2-300x169.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 871px) 100vw, 871px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh WTC Gateway quy m\u00f4 168.000m2, n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t tuy\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 ga trung t\u00e2m<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean, D\u1ef1 \u00e1n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n Ph\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean gia Ecolux City do C\u00f4ng ty CP Kinh doanh v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (TDC) l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea7u, h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ecolux City t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c ngay m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ed9 L\u00ea\u202fL\u1ee3i, t\u1ea1i ph\u01b0\u1eddng H\u00f2a\u202fPh\u00fa, Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Th\u1ee7 D\u1ea7u M\u1ed9t \u2013 trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a TP M\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. D\u1ef1 \u00e1n gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi 119 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi 2-3 m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t, n\u1eb1m trong khu \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb quy ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n r\u1ed9ng 16,8 ha. M\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u1ea5p, kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u01b0 d\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong chu\u1ed7i \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb, c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p quy m\u00f4 1.000 ha, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh khu v\u1ef1c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-1646\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"942\" height=\"464\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-3.jpeg 1920w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-3-300x148.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-3-1024x504.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-3-768x378.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/bai-viet-3-1536x756.jpeg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 942px) 100vw, 942px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh d\u1ef1 \u00e1n Ecolux City<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">V\u1edbi h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c, Ecolux City kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u an c\u01b0 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khai th\u00e1c kinh doanh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. D\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i, h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia, doanh nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ti\u1ec7n \u00edch n\u1ed9i &amp; ngo\u1ea1i khu c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111a d\u1ea1ng khi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi B\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n V\u1ea1n Ph\u00fac 1, H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf li\u00ean c\u1ea5p Singapore &amp; Vi\u1ec7t Hoa, \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Mi\u1ec1n \u0110\u00f4ng, C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean 75ha, Trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i Sora Garden (Si\u00eau th\u1ecb AEON), Khu ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p WTC Gateway, c\u00e1c s\u00e2n Golf cao c\u1ea5p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n nghi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u1ea7ng l\u1edbp chuy\u00ean gia v\u00e0 doanh nh\u00e2n trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi.<\/span><b> \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 4 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u0103n shophouse v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1, k\u00e8m chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 6,5%, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 g\u00f3i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n nh\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u v\u00e0 qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng booking s\u1edbm, thanh to\u00e1n ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 2 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c ngay <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ea1nh tranh so v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 trung b\u00ecnh Shophouse t\u1ea1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (8-12 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/c\u0103n).<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0103n gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u2013 Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef su\u1ea5t ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n!<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Website: https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn. Hotline: 0913 98 98 88<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vi\u1ec7c s\u00e1t nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ecba gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd v\u00e0o TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &#8220;V\u00e0nh \u0111ai \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u2013 c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p&#8221;, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u00e1c &#8220;v\u1ec7 tinh&#8221; \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb ki\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Thu\u1ed9c tam gi\u00e1c kinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi TP HCM [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":1649,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"rank_math_lock_modified_date":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1645","post","type-post","status-publish","format-st